profile:
Service With a Good Reputation
John G. Plumbing Inc. was established with a good reputation and to make a difference in the industry of plumbing. With our years of experience as well as well-trained technicians, we take pride in delivering top-notch quality services, which give us an edge in the Mid-Island area from Nanaimo to Qualicum Beach.

All your plumbing needs and services including; Repiping Services, Drainage Cleaning, Clogged Toilet Repair, Drain & Sewer Cleaning, Hydro-jetting, Camera Inspection, Line Locating, General Plumbing and Renovations
Burst Pipe Repair, Appliance hook-ups, Kitchen Plumbing, Toilet Repair, Gas & Hot Water, Water Heaters, Tankless water heaters, BBQ Box Installation and Fire Pit Installation.
services:
Best-in-class technicians
Uniformed and Professional Team
Meticulous care
100% Happy and Satisfied Customer Guarantee
brands: Navien, Rinnai, Rheem, Bradford White, John Wood,
specialities:
The John G. Difference
At John G. Plumbing, we provide plumbing solutions differently. We always serve with a smile and we make sure that all of our services are served in accordance to our standards. That is the reason why our customer service is always available to answer all your concerns or questions regarding what we offer and how we can help you.
payment_method: Cash, Cheque, Major Credit Cards and e-transfer
warranty_terms: Usually 1 year on labour and manufacturer's warranty on material
